          alt="Roys, a hand-raised male Congo African Grey parrot, four months old, perched and looking toward the camera"
          width="640" height="640"
          class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-lg object-cover"
          loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-gold text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Psittacus erithacus &middot; CITES Appendix I Captive-Bred</p>
        <h1 class="font-lora font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-5">Roys — Male Congo African Grey For Sale ($2,300, Hand-Raised &amp; DNA-Sexed)</h1>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">Roys is a hand-raised male Congo African Grey for sale at $2,300, four months old, captive-bred here in the USA. He is an energetic, playful boy we raised from the start — the kind of grey who wants toys to shred, problems to solve, and people around to share it all. He is DNA-sexed, CITES Appendix I documented, raised in our USDA AWA licensed family aviary, and ready to reserve with a $200 deposit.</p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-cream/90 mb-7">
