      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 3 — AEO "BIRD SNAPSHOT" BOX (featured-snippet target) */}
  <section class="py-12 px-4 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-2xl text-logo-dark mb-3">Roys at a glance — Male Congo African Grey for Sale Snapshot</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Roys is a hand-raised male Congo African Grey (<em>Psittacus erithacus</em>), 4 months old, priced at $2,300. He is DNA-sexed, CITES-documented, captive-bred in the USA at our USDA AWA licensed aviary, and ships nationwide ($185 airport / $350 home).</p>
